company_name: FIMEX TIEFKÜHL GMBH IMPORT UND EXPORT VON FISCHEN
information: The company FIMEX TIEFKÜHL GMBH IMPORT UND EXPORT VON FISCHEN, is a Manufacturer/ Producer, founded in 1978, which operates in the Fish industry. It also operates in the Shellfish and crustaceans industries. It is based in Bremerhaven, Germany.
